1. To update the history_*.dat file
===================================

To extract the previous days data from bugzilla and append it to 
the end of the monthly history file:

    ./daily.py >> history_jul.dat

To do this for a specific date retroactively, you can sepcify the
date in ISO format:

    ./daily.py 2007-07-12 >> history_jul.dat

The updated histriy file should be checked back to SVN time to time,
so that it does not get lost.


2. To generate the dashboard chart
==================================

To generate the image in EPS (default) format from the history data file(s),
run the following:

    ./make_chart.py history_*.dat

The above will print the PS content to the stdout. You can capture it in
either of two ways:

    ./make_chart.py --output=somefile.eps history_*.dat
    
    or the old fashioned Unix way
    
    ./make_chart.py history_*.dat > somefile.eps
    
You can generate other formats too (png, pdf, svg, x11). Examples:

    ./make_chart.py --format=pdf --output=somefile.pdf
    ./make_chart.py --format=png --output=somefile.png
    
